data.description:
Welcome to 7 Coty Lane, Mapleton, ME 04757! This property offers a warm place to stay in Maine, with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, perfect for a growing family!

Discover the perfect blend of convenience and comfort at 7 Coty Lane, Mapleton, ME 04757. This 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch offers easy maintenance, one-floor living, and a fantastic location. The open concept living area, master bedroom with on-suite bath, and ample storage space make it a true gem. With a full basement and additional 2.4 acres of land, the possibilities are endless. Don't miss out on this opportunity - contact us today!
